=== 头设 ===
[[File:Google_Daydream_Concept_Art.jpeg|缩略图]]
Google Daydream View与首款Daydream头设在2016年10月4日宣布<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blog.google/products/google-vr/daydream-bringing-high-quality-vr-everyone/|title=Daydream: Bringing high-quality VR to everyone|accessdate=2016-11-22|date=2016-10-04|last=Bavor|first=Clay|publisher=Google|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212211633/https://blog.google/products/google-vr/daydream-bringing-high-quality-vr-everyone/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/digital/news/google-daydream-headset-79-dollars-1201876438/|title=Google to Unveil First Daydream Virtual Reality Headset Tuesday, Likely Priced $79 (EXCLUSIVE)|accessdate=2016-11-22|date=2016-10-03|last=Roettgers|first=Janko|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206172208/https://variety.com/2016/digital/news/google-daydream-headset-79-dollars-1201876438/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Daydream goes on sale next month">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/10/4/13161506/google-vr-headset-photos-daydream-view-virtual-reality|title=Google's Daydream View VR headset goes on sale next month for $79|accessdate=2016-11-22|date=2016-10-04|last=Robertson|first=Adi|publisher=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007203651/http://www.theverge.com/2016/10/4/13161506/google-vr-headset-photos-daydream-view-virtual-reality|dead-url=no}}</ref>。把支持Daydream的智能手机放入Daydream View前部的格子后，用户便可以通过Daydream View的2个镜头看到VR图像。与此前众多VR头设不同，Daydream View由轻质布料制成，手机格有两个带有电容性的纽扣状小块，它们可与内置[[近場通訊|NFC]]芯片配合，简化虚拟现实环境的设置过程<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2016/10/daydream-vr-hands-on-googles-dumb-vr-headset-is-actually-very-clever/|script-title=en:Daydream VR hands-on: Google’s “dumb” VR headset is actually very clever|accessdate=2016-11-22|date=2016-10-05|last=Amadeo|first=Ron|publisher=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121185808/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2016/10/daydream-vr-hands-on-googles-dumb-vr-headset-is-actually-very-clever/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年11月10日，Daydream View正式发布。<ref name="Daydream View November 10" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/11/1/13489018/google-daydream-view-headset-release-date-november-10|script-title=en:Google’s Daydream VR headset is coming November 10th|accessdate=2016-11-22|date=2016-11-01|last=Robertson|first=Adi|publisher=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108093350/http://www.theverge.com/2016/11/1/13489018/google-daydream-view-headset-release-date-november-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

